## Quality Gates

**Midjourney/Canva visual prompts must pass all quality gates**:

- ✅ **Vision mockup prompt provided** (for persona or opportunity)
- ✅ **Conceptual diagram prompt provided** (for persona or opportunity)
- ✅ **Social ad concept prompts provided** (for persona or opportunity)
- ✅ **Prompts are detailed** (include all key elements)
- ✅ **Tool specified** (Midjourney or Canva)
- ✅ **Usage documented** (how to use the visual)
- ✅ **Visual empathy artifact created** (helps understanding and communication)

## Non-Negotiables

- **Vision mockup prompt required** - Cannot skip vision mockup
- **Conceptual diagram prompt required** - Cannot skip conceptual diagram
- **Social ad concept prompts required** - Cannot skip social ad concepts
- **Tool must be specified** - Must specify Midjourney or Canva
- **Prompts must be detailed** - Must include all key elements
- **Visual empathy artifact required** - Must help understanding and communication

